{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we were in our particular section, we kept ourselves to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were not allowed out, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My parents had to work there, and the work was much worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father worked in what they called a shoe kommando, where they had a big tent, and they accumulated lots of shoes from all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the job of these people was to take the shoes apart and salvage the leather.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Germans were great ones for salvaging everything, because they were an island nation, in a way, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Cut off all the way around, kind of thing, and they needed everything they could get, in way of materials and rubber and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so they wanted to salvage all the leather on the shoes, and that was a job in this Belsen shoe kommando.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father worked in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was obviously totally unsuitable for that sort of work, having been a musician and a bank manager, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And not really suitable for that sort of practical work, so obviously didn't enjoy it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know what my mother did-- presumably maybe worked in the kitchens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Many of the women worked in the kitchen, peeling potatoes, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not have to work in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember quite distinctly, although we didn't-- don't have any documents from Belsen at all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we have documents afterwards, saying that we were in Belsen, but in Belsen, itself, there were no documents.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
